	<h2><TMPL_VAR NAME="PAGE_TITLE"> Tips</h2>

        <p>Not all states require the same information to conduct a search. It is best to input as much information as you have and then choose which state you wish to conduct your search in. Required input fields will highlight based on the selected state.  If you are unable to fill in the required field, you will not be allowed to proceed with a search within that state.</p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>

	<p>Results vary from state to state but may include:</p>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>

	<ol id="font81">
	  <li>General Information - such as the drivers license number, drivers license state, drivers license status and other information normally found on the drivers license.<br />
          <br /></li>
	  <li>Activity Information - such as violations, accidents, suspensions or any other activity relating to the drivers license.<br/>
	  <br /></li>
        </ol>


